记载都烧掉了","可能是个小部族，史官没记下来","你的铭文被后人改过啦"],["C","A","B"],["\"我身上的铭文写着'季之白歸'...每次有人念出这几个字，我都能感觉到铸造时铜水沸腾的温度。但让我困惑的是，为什么那些学者说我是'最早的升鼎'，这意味着什么？\""," \"有个记忆片段很模糊...很多人围着我跪拜，空气中弥漫着香料的味道。但我内壁的铭文却写着'子孙永宝用之'...这是不是说，我原本不该出现在祭祀场合？\"","\"我出土的地方据说属于'汉阳诸姬'...但为什么我的铭文中提到的'邦国'在史书上找不到记载？是我被遗忘了吗？还是说...我的主人本就是历史中的一个谜？\""],-2,[3,"7ajYD5+/FGXprlRyj5owJs"],0,1,2,3,4,5,6]],[4,"c8NOycGYxB27Ry31Op6wbU",null,null,null,-1,0]]],0,[0,1,1,0,2,1,0,3,1,2],[0,0,0,0,0,0,0],[4,5,6,7,8,9,10],[1,2,3,4,5,6,7]],[[{"name":"bangji-da","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":662,"height":561},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":662,"height":561},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-331,-280.5,0,331,-280.5,0,-331,280.5,0,331,280.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,561,662,561,0,0,662,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-331,"y":-280.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":331,"y":280.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[0],0,[0],[0],[8]],[[{"name":"bangji-hui","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":494,"height":523},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":494,"height":523},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-247,-261.5,0,247,-261.5,0,-247,261.5,0,247,261.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,523,494,523,0,0,494,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-247,"y":-261.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":247,"y":261.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[0],0,[0],[0],[9]],[[{"name":"kapian-bangji-d","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":276,"height":499},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":276,"height":499},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-138,-249.5,0,138,-249.5,0,-138,249.5,0,138,249.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,499,276,499,0,0,276,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-138,"y":-249.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":138,"y":249.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[0],0,[0],[0],[10]],[[{"name":"kapian-bangj